Simplified Mesh:

1. Cylinder[radius, height, radialSegmentCount, heightSegmentCount]
  - goes from 0..height in direction (0,1,0)
2. Generate triangles
3. Generate SCNGeometry object
4. Cylinder goes from a->b: height = distance(a,b). calculate rotation from (0,1,0) to (b-a) using
  - https://math.stackexchange.com/questions/180418/calculate-rotation-matrix-to-align-vector-a-to-vector-b-in-3d

